description: During the fourth Pacific Women Shaping Pacific Development PNG Annual Learning workshop, David Kulimbao, Project Coordinator at Community Development Workers Association Inc (CDWAI), and Pas Semai Linbao, Team Leader of the Tsak Rural Women Empowerment Foundation, reflected on their resilience and food production project.
name: Kirapim Kaikai na Maket Project - Tsak Valley, Papua New Guinea
